(135, 64, 'content', 'Mitts Plastic Surgery in Bakersfield, California, is a specialist clinic founded and run by Gordon Mitts, MD, a plastic surgeon with more than 20 years of experience in cosmetic and reconstructive surgery. Dr. Mitts and his aesthetician, Lisa Murphy, RN, aim to provide every patient with the highest quality treatment and care, and the clinic bases its ethos on helping patients achieve their cosmetic and reconstructive goals.\r\n\r\nDr. Mitts comes from a family of physicians, including his father and two uncles, and after graduating from La Sierra University in Riverside, California, he pursued his own calling into the field of medicine. He obtained his medical degree from Loma Linda University Medical Center, California, and gained extensive experience in a series of surgical residency positions before opening Mitts Plastic Surgery in Bakersfield.\r\n\r\nDr. Mitts understands the importance of educating himself on the most advanced treatment options available and the latest technological developments to optimize the patient experience and increase patient comfort and safety while reducing healing time. He uses the most effective, state-of-the-art treatments at Mitts Plastic Surgery, such as the SMAS face-lift that targets underlying muscle for a natural-looking result, and minimally invasive ultrasonic liposuction that aids fat removal.\r\n\r\nDr. Mitts and his team want to help you feel happier, healthier, and more confident so you can enjoy your life to the fullest, and they pride themselves on providing both excellent patient care and refined aesthetic results.'),
