(1155, 54, '_procedures_1_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(1156, 54, 'procedures_1_procedures_content', 'Even patients who have healthy diet and exercise habits can have trouble maintaining an ideal shape. Problem areas of the body such as the stomach, thighs, and buttocks can be resistant to change and hinder a patient’s appearance. Using the latest and safest treatment methods, Dr. Mitts performs a number of body enhancing procedures that can alter the silhouette, creating a youthful, sculpted physique.'),
