(1176, 54, 'procedures_2_procedures_heading2', '<h4>Facial Rejuvenation</h4>'),
(1177, 54, '_procedures_2_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(1178, 54, 'procedures_2_procedures_content', 'The face is the most distinctive part of the body, and its features have an undeniable impact on a patient’s overall look. Through facial plastic surgery, Dr. Mitts can help Tulare County patients bring their facial features into balance and harmony, and combat signs of aging. Using the most advanced and effective surgical techniques, along with his well-trained aesthetic eye, Dr. Mitts can produce beautiful, refined results for your most delicate features.'),
