(1183, 54, '_procedures_3_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(1184, 54, 'procedures_3_procedures_content', 'Many patients would like to alter their appearance but are apprehensive about undergoing surgery. In these instances, Dr. Mitts is able to administer minimally invasive, non-surgical treatments that can drastically improve a patient’s appearance. From facial peels to refresh the skin to injectable treatments for a youthful boost, Dr. Mitts can provide for the diverse cosmetic needs of all patients.'),
(1185, 54, '_procedures_3_procedures_content', 'field_5cc942a30d115'),
