(1189, 54, '_procedures_4_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(1190, 54, 'procedures_4_procedures_content', 'Many men and women spend a significant amount of time, money, and energy seeking products that can reduce the signs of aging, eliminate blemishes, and help them appear younger and more vibrant. Unfortunately, many over-the-counter products over-promise, and under-deliver. With professional facial products and creams, Dr. Mitts can provide patients with real results that are both long lasting and natural looking.'),
