(1476, 170, 'procedures_0_procedures_heading1', '<h2>Turn Heads with a New Look</h2>'),
(1477, 170, '_procedures_0_procedures_heading1', 'field_5cc942210d113'),
(1478, 170, 'procedures_0_procedures_heading2', '<h4>Breast Enhancements</h4>'),
(1479, 170, '_procedures_0_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(1480, 170, 'procedures_0_procedures_content', 'Breast size and shape can play a major role in a woman’s self-esteem and sense of femininity. Many women wish to alter the breasts to achieve a youthful, attractive appearance. While for some this may involve enhancing the size of their breasts, other women may desire a reduction, or a breast lift. Dr. Mitts understands that each patient’s cosmetic goals are different, and works with patients individually to provide them with cosmetic surgery that can produce beautiful, long-lasting results. In addition, Dr. Mitts has performed countless breast reconstruction procedures for post-mastectomy patients, restoring their appearance, confidence, and sense of self.'),
(1481, 170, '_procedures_0_procedures_content', 'field_5cc942a30d115'),
(1482, 170, 'procedures_1_procedures_heading1', ''),
(1483, 170, '_procedures_1_procedures_heading1', 'field_5cc942210d113'),
(1484, 170, 'procedures_1_procedures_heading2', '<h4>Body Contouring</h4>'),
(1485, 170, '_procedures_1_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(1486, 170, 'procedures_1_procedures_content', 'Even patients who have healthy diet and exercise habits can have trouble maintaining an ideal shape. Problem areas of the body such as the stomach, thighs, and buttocks can be resistant to change and hinder a patient’s appearance. Using the latest and safest treatment methods, Dr. Mitts performs a number of body enhancing procedures that can alter the silhouette, creating a youthful, sculpted physique.'),
(1487, 170, '_procedures_1_procedures_content', 'field_5cc942a30d115'),
(1488, 170, 'procedures', '6'),
(1489, 170, '_procedures', 'field_5cc942190d112'),
(1490, 170, 'procedures_2_procedures_heading1', ''),
(1491, 170, '_procedures_2_procedures_heading1', 'field_5cc942210d113'),
(1492, 170, 'procedures_2_procedures_heading2', '<h4>Facial Rejuvenation</h4>'),
(1493, 170, '_procedures_2_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(1494, 170, 'procedures_2_procedures_content', 'The face is the most distinctive part of the body, and its features have an undeniable impact on a patient’s overall look. Through facial plastic surgery, Dr. Mitts can help Tulare County patients bring their facial features into balance and harmony, and combat signs of aging. Using the most advanced and effective surgical techniques, along with his well-trained aesthetic eye, Dr. Mitts can produce beautiful, refined results for your most delicate features.'),
(1495, 170, '_procedures_2_procedures_content', 'field_5cc942a30d115'),
(1496, 170, 'procedures_3_procedures_heading1', ''),
(1497, 170, '_procedures_3_procedures_heading1', 'field_5cc942210d113'),
(1498, 170, 'procedures_3_procedures_heading2', '<h4>Non-Surgical Treatments</h4>'),
(1499, 170, '_procedures_3_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(1500, 170, 'procedures_3_procedures_content', 'Many patients would like to alter their appearance but are apprehensive about undergoing surgery. In these instances, Dr. Mitts is able to administer minimally invasive, non-surgical treatments that can drastically improve a patient’s appearance. From facial peels to refresh the skin to injectable treatments for a youthful boost, Dr. Mitts can provide for the diverse cosmetic needs of all patients.'),
(1501, 170, '_procedures_3_procedures_content', 'field_5cc942a30d115'),
(1502, 170, 'procedures_4_procedures_heading1', ''),
(1503, 170, '_procedures_4_procedures_heading1', 'field_5cc942210d113'),
(1504, 170, 'procedures_4_procedures_heading2', '<h4>Facial Products</h4>'),
(1505, 170, '_procedures_4_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(1506, 170, 'procedures_4_procedures_content', 'Many men and women spend a significant amount of time, money, and energy seeking products that can reduce the signs of aging, eliminate blemishes, and help them appear younger and more vibrant. Unfortunately, many over-the-counter products over-promise, and under-deliver. With professional facial products and creams, Dr. Mitts can provide patients with real results that are both long lasting and natural looking.'),
(1507, 170, '_procedures_4_procedures_content', 'field_5cc942a30d115'),
(1508, 170, 'procedures_5_procedures_heading1', ''),
(1509, 170, '_procedures_5_procedures_heading1', 'field_5cc942210d113'),
(1510, 170, 'procedures_5_procedures_heading2', '<h4>Aesthetic and Laser Services</h4>'),
(1511, 170, '_procedures_5_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(1512, 170, 'procedures_5_procedures_content', 'Dr. Gordon Mitts and staff are here to help you achieve your aesthetic goals. The advancements in Aesthetics and Stem cell products has created a more patient friendly with desirable results with less downtime and more benefits. Our PRP treatments help illuminate the face and give you a more beautiful complexion. It acts as a filler and minimizes the look of fine lines and wrinkles. The skin becomes very subtle and glowing.\r\n\r\nOur Laser Treatments remove the top layer of skin and deeper. This helps to smooth and remove discoloration that is unattractive. We want your experience to be a comfortable with pleasing results.'),
(1513, 170, '_procedures_5_procedures_content', 'field_5cc942a30d115'),
