(4668, 62, 'doctor_0_doctor_heading', '<h2>Ultrasonic Liposuction and Fat Grafting</h2>'),
(4669, 62, '_doctor_0_doctor_heading', 'field_5ccab67b00854'),
(4670, 62, 'doctor_0_doctor_content', 'Although most patients are solely concerned with removing fat from the body, fat grafting is a cosmetic procedure which can improve patient appearances by strategically adding fat to areas of the body that have lost volume and elasticity. Dr. Gordon Mitts offers facial fat grafting which can restore volume to the facial features, helping patients appear youthful and vibrant. This procedure involves the removal of fat from one area of the body, and placing it into targeted areas of the face. Facial fat grafting can be performed as an alternative to some of the non-surgical facial treatments offered at our Bakersfield practice. Ultrasonic liposuction has been shown to be an ideal method for harvesting fat from other areas of the body, with nearly 80 percent of fat removed deemed usable for grafting.'),
(4671, 62, '_doctor_0_doctor_content', 'field_5ccab68e00855'),
(4672, 62, 'doctor_1_doctor_heading', '<h2>The Benefit of Ultrasonic Liposuction</h2>'),
(4673, 62, '_doctor_1_doctor_heading', 'field_5ccab67b00854'),
(4674, 62, 'doctor_1_doctor_content', 'Ultrasonic liposuction carries the same benefits as traditional liposuction, but offers its own set of advantages as well. One of the main benefits of ultrasonic liposuction\r\n\r\nis that is considerably less-invasive than traditional liposuction because the fat is liquefied before it is removed from the body. This results in a more gentle procedure, reduced instance of scarring, and faster healing time. Another benefit of ultrasonic liposuction is that the procedure can be used to target fat in several areas of the body. While the procedure is gentle enough to treat areas such as the chin, neck, and arms, it is effective enough to remove fat from the stomach and chest. Because the sound waves liquefy fat prior to removal, ultrasonic liposuction is ideal for particularly dense pockets of fat as well. This makes ultrasonic liposuction a viable alternative to more extensive procedures such as abdominoplasty. Patients who undergo ultrasonic liposuction also find that the skin is tightened during the procedure, eliminating the need for any “fine-tuning” procedures after surgery.\r\n\r\nSome other benefits of ultrasonic liposuction include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Improved appearance</li>\r\n 	<li>Increased self-confidence</li>\r\n 	<li>Health benefits as a result of fat loss</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(4675, 62, '_doctor_1_doctor_content', 'field_5ccab68e00855'),
(4676, 62, 'doctor_2_doctor_heading', '<h2>Contact Mitts Plastic Surgery Today</h2>'),
(4677, 62, '_doctor_2_doctor_heading', 'field_5ccab67b00854'),
(4678, 62, 'doctor_2_doctor_content', 'Dr. Gordon Mitts is dedicated to providing advanced surgical treatments that are safe and effective so his patients can enjoy the body they’ve always wanted. To learn more about the minimally invasive treatments available at Mitts Plastic Surgery, including ultrasonic liposuction, contact our Bakersfield, California practice today.'),
