(4866, 462, 'doctor_heading', '<h2>Sculpt Your Perfect Body</h2>'),
(4867, 462, '_doctor_heading', 'field_5cca7375ba67d'),
(4868, 462, 'doctor_content', '<div class=\"col-lg-12 mt-50\">\r\n<div class=\"doctor-text\">\r\n\r\nFor Dr. Gordon Mitts, being a plastic surgeon is more than just a job, it’s a passion. He understands that many individuals are unhappy with certain aspects of their appearance, and takes great pride in his ability to help patients achieve their cosmetic goals. Dr. Mitts gets to know his patients as individuals so that he can fully understand their unique needs and desires. This dedication to the highest level of patient care, coupled with the use of the latest treatment techniques and tools, has allowed Dr. Mitts to achieve stunning cosmetic results for patients for more than 20 years. By offering a wide range of body sculpting treatments at his Bakersfield , California practice, Dr. Mitts gives all of his patients the opportunity to have the body of their dreams.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in enhancing your appearance through body contouring procedures, contact Mitts Plastic Surgery serving Bakersfield and Tulare County today to see for yourself how the friendly, individualized care from Dr. Mitts and his staff can help you make your ideal body a reality.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 mt-20\">\r\n<div class=\"doctor-text\">\r\n<h2>Liposuction</h2>\r\nDr. Mitts strives to offer the most advanced and effective, least invasive body sculpting treatments to his Bakersfield patients. He is pleased to perform both internal and external ultrasonic liposuction. Like traditional liposuction, ultrasonic liposuction removes unwanted fat from several areas of the body. However, this advanced technique uses high-pitched sound waves to liquefy fat prior to removal, enhancing Dr. Mitts’ ability to remove particularly dense pockets of fat. Ultrasonic liposuction can simultaneously tighten the skin, making it a preferred treatment option for patients who do not want to undergo multiple surgical procedures.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 mt-20\">\r\n<div class=\"doctor-text\">\r\n<h2>Tummy Tuck</h2>\r\nFor many individuals, stubborn belly fat is holding them back from their ideal body. A tummy tuck, also referred to as abdominoplasty, is a comprehensive body contouring procedure that removes fat from the abdomen and tightens underlying muscles, resulting in a sleek, attractive look. Not only can a tummy tuck help patients fit into smaller sizes, but it can also drastically improve their self-confidence. Dr. Mitts also offers the mini-tummy tuck for less of an extended scar. Call to see if you qualify for this surgery.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 mt-20\">\r\n<div class=\"doctor-text\">\r\n<h2>Thigh Lift</h2>\r\nLoose, excess skin on the upper legs can be a cause for self-consciousness, especially among women. The thigh lift procedure can eliminate fat in the thighs and tighten the skin, giving patients a slender, healthy appearance. This body sculpting procedure can target both the inner and outer thighs, and is ideal for patients who have experienced weight fluctuations. Many patients choose to combine this treatment with other procedures such as gluteal implants, or a butt lift.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 mt-20\">\r\n<div class=\"doctor-text\">\r\n<h2>Gluteal Implants</h2>\r\nDr. Mitts offers gluteal implants, also known as butt implants, to his Bakersfield patients who desire a shapely figure. Gluteal implants are made of silicone and can vary in size and shape based on individual preference. In addition to adding curves to the body, gluteal implants give patients more clothing options and help them feel confident about their shape.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 mt-20\">\r\n<div class=\"doctor-text\">\r\n<h2>More Information on Body Sculpting</h2>\r\nWhen patients feel good about their bodies, it can enhance their lives in so many ways. It is the ability to improve his patients’ lives that makes Dr. Mitts so passionate about plastic surgery. If you would like to learn more about how body sculpting procedures at Dr. Mitts’ Bakersfield practice can transform your life, contact Mitts Plastic Surgery today.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
