(6967, 638, 'doctor_4_doctor_content', 'Breast reconstruction following mastectomy can help women regain their sense of self after breast cancer. Dr. Mitts and his team are experts in several reconstructive techniques including latissimus flap, TRAM flap, and implant reconstruction. Each of these procedures offers its own unique set of benefits, and can effectively rebuild a woman’s breast and restore her confidence. Dr. Mitts works closely with the patient’s breast cancer surgeon to devise the safest, most efficient treatment plan possible.\r\n\r\nThis collaboration also gives Dr. Mitts the opportunity to perform implant reconstruction immediately after mastectomy, should the patient choose. In addition, Dr. Mitts is able to perform nipple reconstruction, a finishing touch to breast reconstruction that significantly contributes to creating a natural-looking result.'),
(6968, 638, '_doctor_4_doctor_content', 'field_5ccabbc2f0134'),
(6969, 638, 'doctor_5_doctor_heading', '<h4>Breast Reduction</h4>'),
(6970, 638, '_doctor_5_doctor_heading', 'field_5ccabbb0f0133'),
(6971, 638, 'doctor_5_doctor_content', 'Breast reduction surgery removes excess skin, fat, and tissue from the breast area in an effort to create a well-proportioned figure for female patients. When the breasts are particularly large, women can often experience discomfort, poor posture, and diminished self-esteem. By reducing the size of the breasts, Dr. Mitts can completely transform a patient’s figure, alleviate daily aches and pains, and enhance her self-confidence. The results of breast reduction surgery often mimic a breast lift, helping patients appear more youthful, as well. Because oversized breasts sometimes lead to health problems, the cost of the breast reduction procedure may be at least partially covered by insurance.'),
(6972, 638, '_doctor_5_doctor_content', 'field_5ccabbc2f0134'),
(6973, 638, 'doctor_6_doctor_heading', '<h2>Learn More about Breast Surgery</h2>'),
(6974, 638, '_doctor_6_doctor_heading', 'field_5ccabbb0f0133'),
(6975, 638, 'doctor_6_doctor_content', 'Enhancing the size and shape of the breast can go a long way toward helping a patient feel confident about her body. Additionally, breast reconstruction surgery following mastectomy has priceless benefits. Dr. Mitts is proud to offer breast surgery at his Bakersfield, California practice because he understands the positive impact that these procedures can have. If you have been considering breast surgery and would like to learn more about the procedures offered at our cosmetic surgery practice, please contact us today.'),
