(7381, 644, 'procedures_0_procedures_heading1', '<h2>Turn Heads with a New Look</h2>'),
(7382, 644, '_procedures_0_procedures_heading1', 'field_5cc942210d113'),
(7383, 644, 'procedures_0_procedures_heading2', '<h4>Breast Enhancements</h4>'),
(7384, 644, '_procedures_0_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(7385, 644, 'procedures_0_procedures_content', 'Breast size and shape can play a major role in a woman’s self-esteem and sense of femininity. Many women wish to alter the breasts to achieve a youthful, attractive appearance. While for some this may involve enhancing the size of their breasts, other women may desire a reduction, or a breast lift. Dr. Mitts understands that each patient’s cosmetic goals are different, and works with patients individually to provide them with cosmetic surgery that can produce beautiful, long-lasting results. In addition, Dr. Mitts has performed countless breast reconstruction procedures for post-mastectomy patients, restoring their appearance, confidence, and sense of self.'),
(7386, 644, '_procedures_0_procedures_content', 'field_5cc942a30d115'),
(7387, 644, 'procedures_1_procedures_heading1', ''),
(7388, 644, '_procedures_1_procedures_heading1', 'field_5cc942210d113'),
(7389, 644, 'procedures_1_procedures_heading2', '<h4>Body Contouring</h4>'),
(7390, 644, '_procedures_1_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(7391, 644, 'procedures_1_procedures_content', 'Even patients who have healthy diet and exercise habits can have trouble maintaining an ideal shape. Problem areas of the body such as the stomach, thighs, and buttocks can be resistant to change and hinder a patient’s appearance. Using the latest and safest treatment methods, Dr. Mitts performs a number of body enhancing procedures that can alter the silhouette, creating a youthful, sculpted physique.'),
(7392, 644, '_procedures_1_procedures_content', 'field_5cc942a30d115'),
(7393, 644, 'procedures', '6'),
(7394, 644, '_procedures', 'field_5cc942190d112'),
