(7396, 644, '_procedures_2_procedures_heading1', 'field_5cc942210d113'),
(7397, 644, 'procedures_2_procedures_heading2', '<h4>Facial Rejuvenation</h4>'),
(7398, 644, '_procedures_2_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(7399, 644, 'procedures_2_procedures_content', 'The face is the most distinctive part of the body, and its features have an undeniable impact on a patient’s overall look. Through facial plastic surgery, Dr. Mitts can help Tulare County patients bring their facial features into balance and harmony, and combat signs of aging. Using the most advanced and effective surgical techniques, along with his well-trained aesthetic eye, Dr. Mitts can produce beautiful, refined results for your most delicate features.'),
(7400, 644, '_procedures_2_procedures_content', 'field_5cc942a30d115'),
(7401, 644, 'procedures_3_procedures_heading1', ''),
(7402, 644, '_procedures_3_procedures_heading1', 'field_5cc942210d113'),
(7403, 644, 'procedures_3_procedures_heading2', '<h4>Non-Surgical Treatments</h4>'),
(7404, 644, '_procedures_3_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(7405, 644, 'procedures_3_procedures_content', 'Many patients would like to alter their appearance but are apprehensive about undergoing surgery. In these instances, Dr. Mitts is able to administer minimally invasive, non-surgical treatments that can drastically improve a patient’s appearance. From facial peels to refresh the skin to injectable treatments for a youthful boost, Dr. Mitts can provide for the diverse cosmetic needs of all patients.'),
(7406, 644, '_procedures_3_procedures_content', 'field_5cc942a30d115'),
(7407, 644, 'procedures_4_procedures_heading1', ''),
(7408, 644, '_procedures_4_procedures_heading1', 'field_5cc942210d113'),
(7409, 644, 'procedures_4_procedures_heading2', '<h4>Facial Products</h4>'),
(7410, 644, '_procedures_4_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(7411, 644, 'procedures_4_procedures_content', 'Many men and women spend a significant amount of time, money, and energy seeking products that can reduce the signs of aging, eliminate blemishes, and help them appear younger and more vibrant. Unfortunately, many over-the-counter products over-promise, and under-deliver. With professional facial products and creams, Dr. Mitts can provide patients with real results that are both long lasting and natural looking.'),
(7412, 644, '_procedures_4_procedures_content', 'field_5cc942a30d115'),
(7413, 644, 'procedures_5_procedures_heading1', ''),
(7414, 644, '_procedures_5_procedures_heading1', 'field_5cc942210d113'),
