(7416, 644, '_procedures_5_procedures_heading2', 'field_5cc942950d114'),
(7417, 644, 'procedures_5_procedures_content', 'Dr. Gordon Mitts and staff are here to help you achieve your aesthetic goals. The advancements in Aesthetics and Stem cell products has created a more patient friendly with desirable results with less downtime and more benefits. Our PRP treatments help illuminate the face and give you a more beautiful complexion. It acts as a filler and minimizes the look of fine lines and wrinkles. The skin becomes very subtle and glowing.\r\n\r\nOur Laser Treatments remove the top layer of skin and deeper. This helps to smooth and remove discoloration that is unattractive. We want your experience to be a comfortable with pleasing results.'),
