(5502, 38, 'doctor_0_doctor_heading', '<h1>Facelift</h1>\r\n<h4>What is breast augmentation?</h4>'),
(5503, 38, '_doctor_0_doctor_heading', 'field_5ccac2bb08955'),
(5504, 38, 'doctor_0_doctor_content', 'Dummy text is text that is used in the publishing industry or by web designers to occupy the space which will later be filled with \'real\' content. This is required when, for example, the final text is not yet available. Dummy text is also known as \'fill text\'.\r\n\r\nDummy text is text that is used in the publishing industry or by web designers to occupy the space which will later be filled with \'real\' content. This is required when, for example, the final text is not yet available. Dummy text is also known as \'fill text\'.'),
(5505, 38, '_doctor_0_doctor_content', 'field_5ccac2ca08956'),
(5506, 38, 'doctor_1_doctor_heading', '<h4>What are the benefits of breast augmentation?</h4>'),
(5507, 38, '_doctor_1_doctor_heading', 'field_5ccac2bb08955'),
(5508, 38, 'doctor_1_doctor_content', 'Breast augmentation offers a number of benefits for women, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Creating a more rounded breast shape</li>\r\n 	<li>Increasing fullness and size of breasts</li>\r\n 	<li>Correcting breast size asymmetry</li>\r\n 	<li>Restoring breast size and shape after weight loss</li>\r\n 	<li>Restoring breast size and shape following pregnancy and breastfeeding</li>\r\n 	<li>Improving the breast and hip ratios to create a well-balanced silhouette</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nUltimately, breast augmentation is designed to improve your self-image and increase your confidence.'),
(5509, 38, '_doctor_1_doctor_content', 'field_5ccac2ca08956'),
(5510, 38, 'doctor_2_doctor_heading', '<h4>How do I book breast augmentation surgery?</h4>'),
(5511, 38, '_doctor_2_doctor_heading', 'field_5ccac2bb08955'),
(5512, 38, 'doctor_2_doctor_content', 'If you think breast augmentation could be a good choice, make an appointment to talk through the options with Dr. Mitts. He reviews your medical history at your consultation, and you can discuss the various factors involved in breast augmentation surgery, such as:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The size and shape of the implants</li>\r\n 	<li>The materials used</li>\r\n 	<li>What happens during the procedure</li>\r\n 	<li>Recovery time</li>\r\n 	<li>What you can expect to achieve from the surgery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDr. Mitts also needs to make sure that you are physically and psychologically fit for the operation and that you have realistic expectations of the results of the surgery.'),
(5513, 38, '_doctor_2_doctor_content', 'field_5ccac2ca08956'),
(5514, 38, 'doctor_3_doctor_heading', '<h4>Does breast augmentation help if my breasts are sagging?</h4>'),
(5515, 38, '_doctor_3_doctor_heading', 'field_5ccac2bb08955'),
(5516, 38, 'doctor_3_doctor_content', 'Breast augmentation can’t fix severely drooping breasts on its own, but Dr. Mitts can assess your suitability for a breast lift operation, or combined breast lift and augmentation procedure. A breast lift raises the breasts, which may or may not then need implants to restore their youthful shape.\r\n\r\nAt your consultation, Dr. Mitts advises you on the best choice between a breast lift and augmentation, or a combination of the two, to ensure you achieve your desired results.'),
(5517, 38, '_doctor_3_doctor_content', 'field_5ccac2ca08956'),
(5518, 38, 'doctor_4_doctor_heading', '<h4>What happens during a breast augmentation operation?</h4>'),
(5519, 38, '_doctor_4_doctor_heading', 'field_5ccac2bb08955'),
(5520, 38, 'doctor_4_doctor_content', 'When you choose Mitts Plastic Surgery for your operation, your comfort is a priority. Dr. Mitts recommends the optimal combination of sedation and anesthesia to keep you comfortable; and, then, when the medications take effect, he makes an incision in an inconspicuous area of your breast to minimize the visibility of the surgical scar.\r\n\r\nAfter making the incision, Dr. Mitts inserts the implant, which can be placed under the pectoral muscle, or behind the breast tissue and over the pectoral muscle. After correctly positioning the implant, Dr. Mitts closes the incision, and your operation is complete.\r\n\r\nYou’ll see the results immediately, but there may be some bruising and swelling, which should disappear within a few days. Dr. Mitts produces natural-looking results that give you the breasts you desire, so book an appointment to discuss breast augmentation surgery by calling Mitts Plastic Surgery today or making an appointment online.'),
(5521, 38, '_doctor_4_doctor_content', 'field_5ccac2ca08956'),
